<h1> Events in Our Space </h1>

<p>
Hollow Earth Radio typically has live events in our space every Friday & Saturday night.
These events are live broadcast online and on 104.9 FM in the Central Area.
Events are also open to the public so come down and hang out in our space while artists perform!
</p>

<p>
A few ground rules:
<ul>
  <li>All of our events are all ages</li>
  <li>Doors typically @ 8 PM unless specified</li>
  <li>$7-15 Suggested Donation, no one turned away for lack of funds</li>
  <li>Our main space is ADA accessible; the bathroom is down a long hallway with one small step down.</li>
  <li>No drugs, no booze, no bad news</li>
</ul>
</p>

<p>
Hollow Earth Radio strives to be a space as safe and welcoming as possible for everyone, with priority to the safety of marginalized identities.
Read about our safer space policy here: <%= link_to "hollowearthradio.org/safer_space" %>
</p>

<p>
Wanna play at Hollow Earth Radio? Easy! Just email us to <%= booking_mailto %>
</p>

